view

Class UI

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.UI

  • public class UI
extends java.lang.Object
    An InteractionManager holds a list of all current Interactions. It handles all commands from the eventHandlers and forwards them to the appriopriate class.
    Author:
    groep 03

      • activateSubwindow

        public ViewInteraction activateSubwindow(int x,
                                         int y)
        Activate a SubWindow (meaning it is moved to the front) if one can be found
        Parameters:
        x - The clicked x coordinates
        y - The clicked y coordinates
        Returns:

        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - Illegal coordinates
